  <h2 class="sec-title" id="weatherTitle">When to Visit <em>Puducherry</em></h2>
  <p class="sec-body" id="weatherNote" style="margin-bottom:0">Puducherry has a tropical coastal climate — warm and humid year-round. November to February is ideal — cool sea breezes, pleasant temperatures (22–30°C), and the northeast monsoon has just ended leaving everything fresh and green. The northeast monsoon (October-December) brings Puducherry its heaviest rains — unlike most of India, Pondy's main rainy season is winter, not summer. March to May gets hot; June-September is dry and windy with rough seas.</p>
